1. *Iste* noći su bile dugačke. (The same nights were long.) 
2. *Istu* knjigu čitam već peti put. (I'm reading the same book for the fifth time.) 
3. Njih dvoje su *isti*. (They two are the same.) 
4. *Istu* rečenicu ponavljala je više puta. (She repeated the same sentence several times.) 
5. *Isto* je bilo i prošle godine. (It was the same last year.)